            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Balancing is the knack for staying steady on narrow or shaky surfaces, like tightropes, crumbling ledges, or storm-swept ship decks. It demands sharp agility and focus to avoid falls or resist being toppled by foes. In battle or hazardous terrains\u2014think icy caves or enchanted spans\u2014this skill keeps characters upright and in control. It\u2019s a must for those who tread the most unstable paths.",
